Syntax and use

1) Declaration

name = Array.create(size)

All values of the array are set to a value.

2) Access

name[number]

3) Multi dimensional arrays

name = Array.create(2)
name[0] = Array.create(2)
name[1] = Array.create(2)

4) Other

Array starts at 0.

Implementation

name[0] =>
LOAD name
ARRAY_VAL 0

---> Load esl::Value* contains in case 0

name[0] = 1 =>
LOAD_INT 1
LOAD name
ARRAY_VAL 0
STORE_STK

ARRAY_VAL i =>

Push in the stack TOS[i]

---

STORE_STK

Perform TOS = TOS1
Pop TOS, but not TOS1
